setRoles(self.portal, TEST_USER_ID, ['Contributor'])
obj = api.content.create(container=self.parent, type=
    'Newsletter Subscriber', id='newsletter_subscriber')
self.assertTrue(INewsletterSubscriber.providedBy(obj),
    u'INewsletterSubscriber not provided by {0}!'.format(obj.id))
self.assertIn('newsletter_subscriber', self.parent.objectIds())
api.content.delete(obj=obj)
self.assertNotIn('newsletter_subscriber', self.parent.objectIds())
